Package: oar-common
Architecture: all
Depends: perl, perl-suid, adduser, libdbi-perl, libdbd-mysql-perl | libdbd-pg-perl
Suggests: oar-server, oar-user, oar-node, oar-doc
Description: OAR batch scheduler common package
 This package installs the common part of the OAR batch scheduler

Package: oar-server
Architecture: all
Depends: oar-common (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, openssh-client | ssh, cron, lsb-base
Recommends: libxml-dumper-perl, libyaml-perl
Suggests: taktuk, mysql-client | postgresql-client, mysql-server | postgresql, phpmyadmin, oar-user, oar-node, oar-doc, openssh-server | ssh
Description: OAR batch scheduler server package
 This package installs the server part of the OAR batch scheduler

Package: oar-scheduler-ocaml-mysql
Architecture: any
Depends: oar-server (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, libmysql-ocaml, libsequel-ruby
Description: OAR batch scheduler package for ocaml scheduler
 This package installs the OCAML scheduler

Package: oar-node
Architecture: all
Depends: oar-common (= ${binary:Version}), openssh-client | ssh, openssh-server | ssh
Suggests: oar-doc, xauth
Description: OAR batch scheduler node package
 This package installs the execution node part of the OAR batch scheduler

Package: oar-user
Architecture: all
Depends: oar-common (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}
Recommends: libxml-dumper-perl, libyaml-perl
Suggests: oar-doc, openssh-client | ssh, xauth
Description: OAR batch scheduler user package
 This package install the submission and query part of the OAR batch scheduler

Package: oar-web-status
Architecture: all
Depends: httpd-cgi, ruby, libdbd-mysql-ruby|libdbd-pg-ruby, libgd-ruby1.8, perl, libdbi-perl, libdbd-mysql-perl | libdbd-pg-perl, libtie-ixhash-perl, libappconfig-perl, libsort-naturally-perl
Suggests: oar-doc
Description: OAR batch scheduler Gantt reservation diagram
 This package install the OAR batch scheduler Gantt reservation diagram CGI: 
 DrawGantt and the instant cluster state visualization CGI: Monika

Package: oar-desktop-computing-agent
Architecture: all
Depends: ruby, oar-common (= ${binary:Version}), libjson-ruby, librestclient-ruby, libdaemons-ruby
Suggests: oar-doc
Description: OAR desktop computing agent
 This package install the OAR batch scheduler desktop computing agent

