 This package install the OAR batch scheduler desktop computing HTTP proxy CGI

Package: oar-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Description: OAR batch scheduler documentation package
 This package install some documentation for OAR batch scheduler

Package: oar-admin
Architecture: all
Depends: oar-user (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, ruby, libdbd-mysql-ruby|libdbd-pg-ruby, libyaml-perl
Suggests: oar-doc, oar-server
Description: OAR batch scheduler administration tools package
 This package installs some useful tools to help the administrator
 of a oar server (resources manipulation, admission rules edition, ...)

Package: oar-api
Architecture: all
Depends: oar-common (>= 2.4.0), oar-user (>= 2.4.0), ${perl:Depends}, httpd-cgi, perl-modules, libjson-perl, libwww-perl
Suggests: oar-doc
Recommends: libxml-simple-perl, libyaml-perl
Description: OAR RESTful API
 This package installs a RESTful API for oar users. 
 It works as a cgi into apache.

Package: oar-gridapi
Architecture: all
Depends: oargrid-client | oar-grid, oar-common (>= 2.4.0), oar-api (= ${binary:Version}) , ${perl:Depends}, httpd-cgi, perl-modules, libjson-perl, libwww-perl
Suggests: oar-doc
Description: OAR RESTful grid api
 This package installs a RESTful API for oargrid users. 
 It works as a cgi into apache.

Package: oar-fix-oldpkg
Architecture: all
Description: Package to fix a buggy postrm script in oar-common
 This package has to be installed only if you upgrade 
 from a version < 2.4.0

Package: oar-keyring
Architecture: all
Description: GnuPG keys of OAR packages maintainers
 This package contains the public keys of the OAR packages
 maintainers.
